# 16. Common Mistakes

---

# Mistake 1 – Wrong Branch Reference

Wrong:

```yaml
if: github.ref == 'main'
```

Correct:

```yaml
if: github.ref == 'refs/heads/main'
```

---

# Mistake 2 – Missing `${{ }}` in Some Cases

Usually not required in `if:`.

Correct:

```yaml
if: github.actor == 'admin'
```

---

# Mistake 3 – Using Secrets in Logs

Bad practice:

```yaml
echo ${{ secrets.API_KEY }}
```

---

# 17. Best Practices

| Best Practice                  | Reason                     |
| ------------------------------ | -------------------------- |
| Use conditions for deployments | Prevent accidental deploys |
| Use `failure()` for alerts     | Better monitoring          |
| Use `always()` for cleanup     | Ensure execution           |
| Use branch checks              | Environment safety         |
| Combine conditions carefully   | Avoid logic errors         |

